title: Russell, Linwood lead No. 5 Baylor past Texas Tech 63-35
text:
> Texas Russell, Linwood lead No. 5 Baylor past Texas Tech 63-35 Texas Tech defensive lineman Branden Jackson (9) pressures the pocket as Baylor quarterback Seth Russell (17) passes in the first half of an NCAA college football game Saturday, Oct. 3, 2015, in Arlington, Texas. (AP Photo/Tony Gutierrez)
